queries.sql: SELECT `product`.`id` as `product_id`, `order`.`id` as `order_id`, `order`.`kode`, CONCAT(client.nama_depan, " ", client.nama_belakang) as client_name, `order`.`logo_tim`, `product`.`nama` as `product_name`, `product`.`picture`, `order_list`.`price`, `order_list`.`status` FROM `order` JOIN `client` ON `client`.`id` = `order`.`id_client` JOIN `order_list` ON `order_list`.`id_order` = `order`.`id` JOIN `product` ON `product`.`id` = `order_list`.`id_product` WHERE `order`.`kode` = 'uq98szad7'
